definition: clauses and sub-clauses (in formal document)/entry (in a dictionary, encyclopedia etc)
strip/item/article/clause (of law or treaty)/classifier for long thin things (ribbon, river, road, trousers etc)

sentences.english: It adds a new entry to the first line in a file.
sentences.chinese: 它在文件的首行添加一个新条目。
这词典有十四万多条目。

sentences.english: Sometimes really ambiguous entries make it on the list because I trust my future self way too much.
sentences.chinese: 有时，我写下含糊不清的条目，这是自视甚高。

sentences.english: You have to edit it quickly for a blog entry, a presentation or your grand-ma, who learned to send emails.
sentences.chinese: 隆重介绍你要编辑的博客条目，很快发送电子邮件。

sentences.english: The entire English section of Wikipedia, dumped into a machine readable format.
sentences.chinese: 维基百科的全部英文条目，转储为机器可读的格式。

sentences.english: There's a third way to access a particular dictionary entry.
sentences.chinese: 访问一个特殊的字典条目还有第三个方法。

sentences.english: Assemble the files and remove the entry from the list.
sentences.chinese: 汇编文件并从列表中删除条目。

sentences.english: The Free Library System (FLS) is a system for maintaining a database of items and borrowers of a library.
sentences.chinese: 是一个用来维护图书馆书刊条目和读者数据库的系统。

sentences.english: It overwrites the entries you added earlier.
sentences.chinese: 它将改写您前面添加的条目。

sentences.english: Each time a function is invoked, you add a new entry to this array.
sentences.chinese: 每次调用函数时，您都将一个新条目添加到该数组中。

sentences.english: The clauses could be subdivided into sub-clauses.
sentences.chinese: 条目之下可再细分为款。

sentences.english: This means every data entry has a parent except the root entry.
sentences.chinese: 这意味着除了根条目之外，每个数据都拥有双亲。

sentences.english: Please select a directory entry shape and then re-execute this command.
sentences.chinese: 请选择目录条目形状，然后重新执行该命令。

sentences.english: It was a stone ip thread.
You can select any number of object classes for an entry.
sentences.chinese: 可以为一个条目选择任意数量的对象类。

sentences.english: FLS - The Free Library System (FLS) is a system for maintaining a database of items and borrowers of a library.
sentences.chinese: 是一个用来维护图书馆书刊条目和读者数据库的系统。
